to the Admiralty, urgent.

86
00:13:35,190 --> 00:13:37,657
Are we absolutely sure
of our position?

87
00:13:39,859 --> 00:13:41,827
Yes, sir. An exact satellite fix.

88
00:14:13,391 --> 00:14:17,192
Captain, we are ready to launch.

89
