it's a Chinese aerial torpedo.

94
00:14:35,912 --> 00:14:37,903
I should report in.

95
00:14:42,519 --> 00:14:46,250
<i>Stamper to Hamburg,
Phase one is in progress,</i>

96
00:14:46,423 --> 00:14:49,085
<i>I'll report back to you
