442
00:41:28,555 --> 00:41:31,547
The key to a great story
is not who...

443
00:41:31,725 --> 00:41:34,193
...or what or when...

444
00:41:35,562 --> 00:41:37,029
...but why.

445
00:41:38,232 --> 00:41:42,531
